{"tid":1498824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（訪港被拒）美軍巨艦穿越台海","createTime":"2019-08-23T13:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T11:53:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":340,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"30c3faf37a735a78237a3d7ea408c4fbcd51410c","tid":1498824,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:54:30.000Z","msg":"台國防部今天證實，兩艘美軍艦艇，今天由南向北穿越台灣海峽，其中一艘開啟AIS，顯示屬於美軍聖安東尼奧級船塢登陸艦。<br />\n<br />\n海軍官校前軍事學科部教官呂禮詩出示美艦發出AIS（船舶自動辨識系統）資料研判，兩艦可能是先前被香港拒絕靠泊的聖安東尼奧級船塢登陸艦「綠灣號」（USS Green Bay LPD 20）和提康德羅加級飛彈巡洋艦「伊利湖號」（USS Lake Erie CG 70）。他認為這是每個月下旬美軍穿越台灣海峽的常態化行動。<br />\n<br />\n聖安東尼奧級是美國海軍新一代的兩棲船塢登陸艦，排水量高達24900噸。<br />\n<br />\n美方宣布售我66桇F-16V戰機，中國大陸外交部21日聲稱，美國對台軍售嚴重違反一中原則，造成的一切後果須完全由美方承擔；美國軍艦今天則再度通過台灣海峽。這是美國軍艦今年來第7度通過台灣海峽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/08/23/realtime/6728164.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F08%2F23%2Frealtime%2F6728164.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=26c8b2f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美軍聖安東尼奧級船塢登陸艦「綠灣號」（USS Green Bay LPD 20）。圖/美國海軍官方網站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4006586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10930%2F4006586&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=005823a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4006586</a>"},{"pid":"af02ac6cb2c12ec7f3ee809236a9601e0a897adf","tid":1498824,"uid":258770,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7b29a04cbf06433b0250c860a5e31c26d7e89a","tid":1498824,"uid":237528,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,